column.name: DESCRIPTION
column.value: tcp.analysis.flags: displays all retransmissions, duplicate acks, zero windows, and more in the trace. Helps when tracking down slow application performance and packet loss

column.name: DESCRIPTION
column.value: tcp.analysis.flags and !tcp.analysis.window_update: displays all retransmissions, duplicate acks, zero windows, and more in the trace. Helps when tracking down slow application performance and packet loss. It will not include the window updates
